==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unscience
<hw>Un*sci"ence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Want of science or
knowledge; ignorance.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If that any wight ween a thing to be otherwise than it is, it is
not only <qex>unscience</qex>, but it is deceivable opinion.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unscrew</ent>⟦br⟧
